<ul><li><a href="http://www.dnaindia.com/analysis/standpoint-how-we-can-transform-youth-activism-into-lasting-civic-engagement-2120002" rel="nofollow">How we can transform youth activism into lasting civic engagement</a> - Swarna Rajagopalan (2015)</li>
